---
title: Thai Beef Strip Stir-fry with green beans and coriander
description: This Thai-inspired beef stir-fry is inspired by the Thai classic 'Pad Krapow Moo'.  Fresh chilli and gingery lemongrass paste provide a bit of bite in this fragrant and exciting dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R16_W09_IE_IECB20966-3_Main_high-af9daf18.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/65723e4f3405d840b2be3d2b.pdf
